it, and the love comes back.

00:16:42.940 --> 00:16:47.890 align:middle line:84%
And other people who visit
enjoy it as well so much.

00:16:47.890 --> 00:16:50.785 align:middle line:84%
So this is a shower that
comes partially from rainfall.

00:16:50.785 --> 00:16:56.970 align:middle line:90%


00:16:56.970 --> 00:16:59.640 align:middle line:84%
It's creating more
uniqueness instead

00:16:59.640 --> 00:17:02.030 align:middle line:84%
of having the old houses
out of ticky tacky,

00:17:02.030 --> 00:17:03.300 align:middle line:90%
you know, every one the same.

00:17:03.300 --> 00:17:06.780 align:middle line:90%


00:17:06.780 --> 00:17:10.440 align:middle line:84%
Variety in life, I think,
is really, really important.

00:17:10.440 --> 00:17:13.500 align:middle line:84%
I've noticed that since
I kind of dropped out

00:17:13.500 --> 00:17:16.680 align:middle line:84%
a little bit from doing
the regular job, my life--

00:17:16.680 --> 00:17:20.670 align:middle line:84%
I can flow and feel
the spirit just taking

00:17:20.670 --> 00:17:22.150 align:middle line:90%
me one way or the other.

00:17:22.150 --> 00:17:27.030 align:middle line:84%
