do, my energy flows into that

00:17:27.030 --> 00:17:30.180 align:middle line:84%
and actually produces
something more beautiful,

00:17:30.180 --> 00:17:32.324 align:middle line:90%
and there's more satisfaction.

00:17:32.324 --> 00:17:35.782 align:middle line:90%


00:17:35.782 --> 00:17:39.734 align:middle line:90%
