be really interesting to be

00:21:39.600 --> 00:21:40.830 align:middle line:90%
inhabited in a way.

00:21:40.830 --> 00:21:44.030 align:middle line:90%


00:21:44.030 --> 00:21:46.680 align:middle line:84%
I was always thinking
about those windows

00:21:46.680 --> 00:21:57.050 align:middle line:84%
